{"tid":345564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[犯我支那者] 蒙古掛台灣國國旗 回應習近平蒙古閱兵","createTime":"2017-08-03T07:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T16:28:12.000Z","uid":54373,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f366f34e3bf313f9877c18baf7099b20baaf18","tid":345564,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/153851_ada58a684d4726e0783518d912916ac9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F153851_ada58a684d4726e0783518d912916ac9.jpg&h=ca16c9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕國際童軍活動「亞太大露營」7月28日於蒙古舉辦，台灣派出114名童軍前往參加。過去許多國際場合因為中國的打壓，使得台灣國旗都無法升起，但蒙古相當大方，讓台灣國旗在會場隨風飄揚！<br />\n從YouTube上的影片可以看到，在傳出鼓聲與吆喝聲的會場上，台灣國旗就佇立在35個與會國家的旗幟之中。據《三立新聞》報導，除了升起國旗之外，台灣童軍還把握站在台上唱名的機會，在舞台用力揮舞國旗。<br />\n報導中指出，台灣小童軍不僅隨身把國旗披在身上，還帶著國旗登山看日出，也不忘合唱國歌。"},{"pid":"b595cac08d068dbf7c25ff470c5643f4c9fff6f6","tid":345564,"uid":126952,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"但係中華民國理論上未放棄蒙古主權  中共先係令蒙古獨立 成件事好怪"},{"pid":"14e0376cd4a38ab83c52cd808e6a4d3f8ed4114c","tid":345564,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e75367262a4ee9bdb2111663cdf227a370c6eb","tid":345564,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:01:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f17a281605c2fd675d03ac4e1fac81fe1db6df74","tid":345564,"uid":41382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係中華民國理論上未放棄蒙古主權  中共先係令蒙古獨立 成件事好怪</blockquote><br />\n中華文國包括mo 古❓</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"a0f2735def38ddf0980a17404db1264822feec80","tid":345564,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"1946年1月5日，中華民國承認外蒙古獨立。但1953年2月24日，中華民國以蘇聯並未做到「不援助中共」等條件認為蘇聯違約在先，故廢除《中蘇友好同盟條約》，改為不承認外蒙古獨立（蒙古人民共和國）。直到2002年，中華民國實質上承認蒙古國，並於對方首都互設具大使館性質的代表機構。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/中華民國與蒙古國關係\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%87%E8%92%99%E5%8F%A4%E5%9C%8B%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82&d=oyvWpG%2BWImCkRdXppRAcizPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=fc695401\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/中華民國與蒙古國關係</a>"},{"pid":"f4ca51d84142c4b1ba4e3ee55bcb6d68d373aa66","tid":345564,"uid":130068,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:23:01.000Z","msg":"台灣國國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哥支叫青天白日滿地紅旗 中華民國國旗🇹🇼"},{"pid":"965b9c45a71e106d08c1ff8cbfb95c3313d826cf","tid":345564,"uid":10890,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係中華民國理論上未放棄蒙古主權  中共先係令蒙古獨立 成件事好怪</blockquote><br />\n中華文國包括mo 古❓</blockquote><br />\n字都唔撚識就死返入你老母個閪啦兔唇五毛賤畜"},{"pid":"ff1e1f8e42f7e6da6e1afe8d952e05bbb8d45431","tid":345564,"uid":78900,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係中華民國理論上未放棄蒙古主權  中共先係令蒙古獨立 成件事好怪</blockquote><br />\n中華文國包括mo 古❓</blockquote><br />\n學下打字先啦屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27be9988324be7330a1b32e25c49168b1f90676","tid":345564,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"屌你，又咁近，叫中共點誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8aa1a4e7791f86fc2e44a2f00a4571539a987b","tid":345564,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"幾時收番主權<br />\n好多支那人有蒙古症"},{"pid":"7505bad8e84603